episodes.title: Cults in the Dark
episodes.description:
There’s an area of society that’s shrouded in layers of darkness and mystery. An area that hides behind fake smiles, promises of “enlightment”, and a false sense of community. Today we’re talking…. Cults. Cults have always fascinated me and I might make this a recurring series. There are some cults I probably won’t touch with a 10 foot pole. Like one that’s always in the news, there was a show about survivors and tons of celebrities are a part of. But there’s plenty we can talk about besides them.

00:00:00 Introduction to Cults
00:03:00 The People's Temple and Jim Jones
00:09:00 Heaven's Gate and Spiritual Transcendence
00:15:00 Digital Cults and Modern Manipulation
00:21:00 Conclusion and Reflections
